《'''眼睛想旅行'''》是香港歌手[[黎明|黎明]]的[[錄音室專輯|錄音室專輯]]，全碟由[[雷頌德|雷頌德]]作曲、編曲及監製<ref>{{Cite book | author = 林玉鑫| title = 百歌爭嗚 成名曲、流行曲快樂大放送 | location = 北京 | publisher = 海潮出版社 | date = 2001-01 | pages = 371 | ISBN = 7801512839 |language = zh-hans}}</ref>，於1999年11月23日由[[索尼音樂娛樂_(香港)|新力唱片]]首次發行<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.881903.com/highlight/2367554/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%88%86%E8%B0%B7-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C/11%E6%9C%8823%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C|title = 11月23日之廣東歌|date = 2020-11-22|publisher = 商業電台|language = zh|accessdate = 2021-06-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210605030306/https://www.881903.com/highlight/2367554/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%88%86%E8%B0%B7-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C/11%E6%9C%8823%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%8C|archive-date = 2021-06-05|dead-url = no}}</ref>，曾登上[[國際唱片業協會（香港會）|香港IFPI]]唱片銷量榜冠軍<ref>{{cite news |language =zh|url = https://i.imgur.com/XSAtg7D.jpg|title = 新碟登IFPI榜首|publisher= 太陽報|author = 沈寶茜 |date = 1999-12-10|accessdate = 2022-03-23|archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220323022945/https://i.imgur.com/XSAtg7D.jpg|archive-date = 2022-03-23|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，截止1999年12月錄得約五萬張銷量<ref>{{cite news |language =zh|url = https://i.imgur.com/LpghZGq.jpg|title = Leon全年收入一覽表|publisher= 太陽報|author = 沈寶茜 |date = 1999-12-05|accessdate = 2022-03-23|archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220323034837/https://i.imgur.com/LpghZGq.jpg|archive-date = 2022-03-23|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，在1999年度香港全年唱片銷量排行第十位<ref>{{cite news |language =zh|url = https://i.imgur.com/ArSuRPJ.jpg|title = 全年唱片銷量前十位排名|publisher= 報章|date = 2000|accessdate = 2022-02-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220204120534/https://i.imgur.com/ArSuRPJ.jpg|archive-date = 2022-02-04|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。這張專輯設有限量特別版，並於2007年8月8日推出重新發行版本。

